subject: Rogers Cup (Tennis)
Tennis
lead_paragraph: Andy Roddick won the 30th title of his career with a 7-6 (7), 6-7 (11), 7-5 victory over Milos Raonic in the Regions Morgan Keegan Championships in Memphis.
